ge.<br /><br />1) Mr Martin spends his spare time engaging in activities that he enjoys.  <br /><br />2) Those people spend their spare time whining about Mr Martin's engaging in activities that he enjoys.<br /><br />LOL.  If I were them then I'd be trying to obscure that fact rather than calling attention to it.  <br /><br />If you are annoying people like that then you must be doing something right!  ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"June 18 2009, 01:00:41 UTC","parent":6399423,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: Hey Mr. Martin","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://alwaysoptimistc.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"alwaysoptimistc","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"alwaysoptimistc","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://alwaysoptimistc.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"alwaysoptimistc","ctime_ts":1245286841,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/70443208/9682409","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?replyto=6400447","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6400447#t6400447","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6400447#t6400447","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6400447#t6400447","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"werthead","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":6400447,"talkid":25001,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6400447#t6400447","upictitle":"werthead: Gowron Happy!","article":"Ex