y the most notable and vocal. Mr. Martin is OF THE PEOPLE, not Above the people, and he would give as much as he got. Ty would prep him :)<br /><br />By the way, I'll be in Ireland during the filming of the mini-series, when is Mr. Martin going to be there? Is it tacky to ask for an autograph at a pub? ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"June 18 2009, 04:41:26 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Hey","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://jpneshewat84.livejournal.com/","striked":1,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"jpneshewat84","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"jpneshewat84","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://jpneshewat84.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"jpneshewat84","ctime_ts":1245300086,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?replyto=6405055","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6405055#t6405055","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6405055#t6405055","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6405055#t6405055","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"lolz_omg_wtf","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://lolz-omg-wtf.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":6405055,"talkid":25019,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/92351.html?thread=6405055#t6405055","upictitle":"lolz_omg_wtf: pic#0","article":"To those doubting Dance will come out at all:<br /><br />You guys really think HBO would invest in ASoIaF if there weren't demonstrable progress on the next installment in the series? I can't see there lawyers no